{
  "stem": "18581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't know that you-- as a Communist-- are interested in nobility, that there was a name of nobility-- well, I really, I think that's beside the point.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, it's not beside the point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am a Communist, but I am also Russian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he was quite-- quite nationalistic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Unless he made use of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think he did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because, well, for him it was just another Jew who calls himself a Trigubov.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we saw that Hitler was going perfectly unopposed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, he was very successful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we couldn't see how he could avoid going especially [? to-- ?] to Lithuania, which was on his way to Moscow-- I mean, to [NON-ENGLISH] and Moscow.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we believed that-- that that will be, actually, the Russian aim-- the-- excuse me-- the German aim.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Lithuanian government?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Lithuanian government was already a Soviet government at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the Soviets, well, on one hand, they expect it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's why they said, at that time, I mean, secretly, to Communists, that we signed the agreement with Hitler because we are not ready yet for war.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they certainly did prepare for war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at the same time, there was a great deal of negligence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was told that the day when Hitler attacked, most Soviet aircraft were unprepared for takeoff because they-- they had-- there was no gasoline.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were-- had-- they had to be inspected.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it could have very well be a German [INAUDIBLE] trick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this, I'm not so sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that-- I'm-- I also not so sure whether I knew it then or I just know it now.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
